OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers will continue through the
OL,7,Fevening but will clear slowly from the
OL,8,Fsouth overnight, becoming largely dry.
OL,9,FIt will become cold as clear spells
OL,10,Fincrease.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FEarly bright spells, a few
OL,13,Fshowers west. Cloud soon spreads north
OL,14,Fwith rain following. This heavy and
OL,15,Fpersistent with snow on the hills. The
OL,16,Fwind strengthens to severe gale later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
