OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,6,Frain, hill snow and severe gales clear
OL,7,FSunday morning, leaving frequent
OL,8,Fshowers. Mostly dry but cloudy Monday
OL,9,Fand Tuesday though with some outbreaks
OL,10,Fof rain at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
